<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GEN-KEISSER-COLUMN-LADN-(SLANG) </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
NICE PLACE TO CALL HOME
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By BOB KEISSER  
 c.1999 Long Beach Press-Telegram  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ It is a little known fact that they had luxury
suites at the Colosseum in Rome. Ask Chick Hearn if you don't
believe me. They weren't very close to the playing field, either,
for perfectly good reasons having to do with wildlife.
</P>
