Yazoo City has ``My Dog Skip'' tours that visit the sites that
Willie Morris wrote about. His cemetery plot is an attraction
itself, buried as he is just 13 steps from the Witch's Grave, the
occupant of which, local legend says, used her black magic to burn
down the town. No reason not to think that eventually he'll be
right up there with Jerry Clower, the country comedian, Yazoo
