<P>
   Y2K-CHEMICAL _ WASHINGTON _ Citing a new report that many
smaller chemical businesses have not prepared for possible year-end
computer disruptions, the chairmen of the Senate Y2K committee
asked federal emergency and environmental officals Thursday to
alert state and local governments to be ``especially vigilant.''
