funky. They never wore masks years ago. Now they're painted and
cool, like Blades goalie Bruce Racine's mask, which features the
Kansas City skyline. Howard Richman 18. Photo
</P>
<P>
   MUFT. The University of Kansas has been looking to this game for
weeks, knowing it could make their season. The University of
Missouri has at least one foot in the same boat. But the Tigers are
new to the boat. Says Kent Layman: Maybe this is what MU needs, to
get a mad on for a team they hate. But maybe that needs to be put
aside in favor of the realization that even if MU beats KU, that is
just the first of three must steps to assure a winning season that
looks iffy at best. Mike DeArmand. 18-20.
