<P>
   INDONESIA-POLITICS (Jakarta, Indonesia) _ In a act of
reconciliation and also of power politics, an emotional national
assembly on Thursday elected the highly popular Megawati
Sukarnoputri to the post of vice president, one day after voting
down her bid for the presidency. By Seth Mydans.
</P>
<P>
   JAPAN-ANCHORWOMAN (Tokyo) _ Since her resignation earlier this
month from Japan's equivalent of the Today Show, Ayumi Kuroda, one
of this country's most popular female television personalities, has
become the subject of a convoluted and much discussed mystery. The
central question remains: did she jump or was she pushed? By Howard
W. French.
</P>
