Man'' as playing ``one note on a piano for two hours and 11
minutes.'' Elisabeth Shue finds more than one note in ``Molly,''
but they all sound like nails being raked across a chalkboard. By
ROBERT PHILPOT. Story has moved in ``e'' entertainment category. &QL; 
