<HEADLINE>
HILLARY CLINTON CITES MORE DIFFERENCES WITH GIULIANI 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDs: FIXES spelling of Clinton in headline)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By STEWART M. POWELL  
 c.1999 Hearst Newspapers  
<TEXT>
<P>
