<HEADLINE>
THE SUN FINALLY RISES: JAPAN INC.'S LOSS IS NIKKEI'S GAIN  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Business Editors)   (This 600-word ``separate buy'' financial story is from the October
issue of ``WORTH'' magazine. To publish this article, it must be
purchased from the New York Times Syndicate's sales representative
DEBRA WEYDERT at 732-390-4480, or fax her at 732-390-4697. Her
e-mail address is weyded(at)nytimes.com. If unable to reach Ms.
Weydert, please call 800-444-0267, or fax us at 816-822-1444.)  
  
 (PLEASE NOTE: This article has been double-filed _ into the ``i''
international news and ``f'' financial news files.)  
  
