down her bid for the presidency, the national assembly elects
Megawati Sukarnoputri, a popular leader of the opposition to the
ousted Suharto regime, to the post of vice president. By Seth
Mydans. (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET in ``a'' news file.) 1,400
words.
