   BUSH-BIOGRAPHY (Washington) _ St. Martin's Press is withdrawing
a new biography of George W. Bush after questions about the book's
allegations of his drug use lead to the discovery that the author
is a convicted felon. By Frank Bruni. (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m.
ET in ``p'' news file.)
