<HEADLINE>
CORRECTION: HOME IMPROVEMENT QUESTIONS AND ANSWERS
</HEADLINE>
  By BERNARD GLADSTONE 
 Copyright 1999 Bernard Gladstone 
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features) 
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS: The Home Improvement Questions and Answers column which
moved Wednesday, Oct. 20, was an old column inadvertently sent in
to the N.Y. Times Syndicate by the writer.
</P>
<P>
   A new column has been transmitted today in its place, with the
main question addressing the installation of `surface wiring' (with
corresponding diagram).
</P>
<P>
   We apologize for any inconvenience.
</P>
