<HEADLINE>
MAKING DRASTIC CHANGES IS LESS LIKELY FOR RANGERS 
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By T.R. SULLIVAN 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
